title: Opie & Jim Norton OCT 19 2015 Mon.mp3
description:
Opie & Jim Norton OCT 19 2015 Mon (03:11:59)


On Today's Show:

Sherrod Small is with Opie and Jimmy. Opie talks about going to a new movie about Steve Jobs, they talk about yesterday's football, Lamar Odom, Jimmy talks about a boxing match he went to with Louis CK, they mention Tracy Morgan on Saturday Night Live over the weekend and Sherrod talks about going to the after-party, and they talk about some college stuff. They talk about Donald Trump and Jeb Bush and participation trophies. They talk about Eddie Murphy receiving an award, Jimmy talks about the new movie The Walk, they talk about urban exploring, they check out part of Amy Schumer's HBO special from over the weekend, Jimmy's old Cribs episode is brought up, and Jimmy goofs around about a Playboy magazine thing they check out
